caption: Cooperative Purchasing
created: 20260318120000000
modified: 20260318120000000
tags: Policy3330(s4)
title: Policy3330(s4)(2)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

This policy will not apply when goods or services are acquired through cooperative purchasing agreements. Primary examples shall include State Contracts, local and regional bids and cooperative bids including but not limited to the Capitol Region Purchasing Council, CREC, CCM, and EASTCONN.
